## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-874">다음 예제에서는 <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XElement>를 <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>에 저장하는 방법을 보여 줍니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-874">The following example shows how to save an <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XElement> to an <xref:System.Xml.XmlWriter>.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
StringBuilder sb = new StringBuilder();  
XmlWriterSettings xws = new XmlWriterSettings();  
xws.OmitXmlDeclaration = true;  
using (XmlWriter xw = XmlWriter.Create(sb, xws)) {  
    XElement root = new XElement("Root",  
        new XElement("Child", "child content")  
    );  
    root.Save(xw);  
}  
Console.WriteLine(sb.ToString());  
```  
  
```vb  
Dim sb As StringBuilder = New StringBuilder()  
Dim xws As XmlWriterSettings = New XmlWriterSettings()  
xws.OmitXmlDeclaration = True  
Using xw = XmlWriter.Create(sb, xws)  
    Dim root As XElement = <Root>  
                               <Child>child content</Child>  
                           </Root>  
    root.Save(xw)  
End Using  
Console.WriteLine(sb.ToString())  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-875">이 예제는 다음과 같은 출력을 생성합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-875">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<Root><Child>child content</Child></Root>  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-919">이 메서드는 특성 집합으로 이름/값 쌍의 목록을 유지 관리 하기 쉬운 되도록 설계 되었습니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-919">This method is designed to make it easy to maintain a list of name/value pairs as a set of attributes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-920">목록을 유지 관리, 쌍을 추가, 쌍을 수정 또는 쌍을 삭제 해야 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-920">When maintaining the list, you need to add pairs, modify pairs, or delete pairs.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-921">존재 하지 않는 이름을 전달 하는 특성으로이 메서드를 호출 하는 경우이 메서드를 특성을 만듭니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-921">If you call this method passing a name that does not exist as an attribute, this method creates an attribute for you.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-922">기존 특성의 이름을 전달 하는이 메서드를 호출 하는 경우이 메서드는 지정 된 값 특성의 값을 수정 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-922">If you call this method passing the name of an existing attribute, this method modifies the value of the attribute to the value that you specify.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-923">전달 하는 경우 `null` 에 대 한 `value`,이 메서드는 특성을 제거 합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-923">If you pass `null` for `value`, this method removes the attribute.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-924">이 메서드를 발생 시킵니다 합니다 <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> 하며 <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> 이벤트입니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-924">This method will raise the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changed> and the <xref:System.Xml.Linq.XObject.Changing> events.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-925">값은 지정 된 이름의 특성에 할당 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-925">The value is assigned to the attribute with the specified name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-926">지정한 이름 가진 특성이 없는 경우에 새 특성이 추가 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-926">If no attribute with the specified name exists, a new attribute is added.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-927">값이 `null`, 지정 된 이름의 특성이 있는 경우 삭제 됩니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-927">If the value is `null`, the attribute with the specified name, if any, is deleted.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-928">자세한 내용은 [이름/값 쌍 유지 관리](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fe9798bf-b5e2-4a3c-a86c-7f8638912691)합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-928">For more information, see [Maintaining Name/Value Pairs](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/fe9798bf-b5e2-4a3c-a86c-7f8638912691).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-929">다음 예제에서는 특성을 사용 하 여 요소를 만듭니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-929">The following example creates an element with an attribute.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-930">그런 다음이 메서드를 사용 하 여 특성의 내용을 바꿉니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-930">It then uses this method to replace the content of the attribute.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an element with no content.  
XElement root = new XElement("Root");  
  
// Add some name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att1", 1);  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 2);  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", 3);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
  
// Modify one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 22);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
  
// Remove one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", null);  
Console.WriteLine(root);  
```  
  
```vb  
' Create an element with no content.  
Dim root As XElement = <Root/>  
  
' Add some name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att1", 1)  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 2)  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", 3)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
  
' Modify one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att2", 22)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
  
' Remove one of the name/value pairs.  
root.SetAttributeValue("Att3", Nothing)  
Console.WriteLine(root)  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="7fdf7-931">이 예제는 다음과 같은 출력을 생성합니다.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="7fdf7-931">This example produces the following output:</span></span>  
  
```  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="2" Att3="3" />  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="22" Att3="3" />  
<Root Att1="1" Att2="22" />  
```
